Sentencas: Nano-structured porous similar to 20 mu m thick LSCF films were fabricated at room temperature for use as cathodes in low temperature operating solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Low-temperature fabrication of nano-structured porous (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3-δ cathodes by aerosol deposition

Sentencas: Fabrication was by the aerosol deposition of ceramic-polymer composite powder.
Titulo: Low-temperature fabrication of nano-structured porous (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3-δ cathodes by aerosol deposition

Sentencas: Various amounts of pore forming polyvinylidene fluoride polymer powder were mixed with LSCF ceramic powder as the starting powder for aerosol deposition.
Titulo: Low-temperature fabrication of nano-structured porous (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3-δ cathodes by aerosol deposition

Sentencas: Increasing polymer content increased the porosity of films and decreased their adhesion strength.
Titulo: Low-temperature fabrication of nano-structured porous (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3-δ cathodes by aerosol deposition

Sentencas: Anode-supported-type cells were created with LSGM electrolyte and nano-structured LSCF cathodes.
Titulo: Low-temperature fabrication of nano-structured porous (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3-δ cathodes by aerosol deposition

Sentencas: The cells' power density was maximized at 0.79 and 1.11 W/cm(2) at 650 and 750 degrees C, respectively, when the starting composite powder contained 5 wt.% polymer.
Titulo: Low-temperature fabrication of nano-structured porous (La,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3-δ cathodes by aerosol deposition
